bubblesort(List, Acc, Sorted) :-

bubble([X,Y|Rest], [Y|NewRest]) :-
    X > Y,
    !,
    bubble([X|Rest], NewRest).
bubble([X,Y|Rest], [X|NewRest]) :-
    bubble([Y|Rest], NewRest).
bubble([X], [X]).
bubble([], []).

forth_sort(L, L2) :- bubblesort(L, [], L2).
